Plot:


Legiunea Straina, este povestea tragicomica a trei tineri rurali, dintr-o localitate in care este declarata gripa aviara. Afacerile merg prost; oricit s-ar fura, nu ajuta la nimic. Dornici sa emigreze, intra in legatura cu afaceristul Maricel (interpretat de Rica Raducanu), care le poate facilita intrarea in Legiunea Straina.

Foreign Legion is the tragi-comic story of three youths from a town that has had an outbreak of the avian flu. Business is poor; no matter how much gets stolen, it doesn't help. Hoping to emigrate, the three strike a deal with Maricel (Rica Raduceanu), who may be able to help them get into the Foreign Legion
